28/*
29 * Command line options
30 */
31int quiet; /* Level of quietness */
32int reservenum; /* Number of memory reservation slots */
33int minsize; /* Minimum blob size */
34int padsize; /* Additional padding to blob */
35int alignsize; /* Additional padding to blob accroding to the alignsize */
36int phandle_format = PHANDLE_BOTH; /* Use linux,phandle or phandle properties */
37int generate_symbols; /* enable symbols & fixup support */
38int generate_fixups; /* suppress generation of fixups on symbol support */
39int auto_label_aliases; /* auto generate labels -> aliases */
40
41static int is_power_of_2(int x)
42{
43 return (x > 0) && ((x & (x - 1)) == 0);
44}
45
46static void fill_fullpaths(struct node *tree, const char *prefix)
47{
48 struct node *child;
49 const char *unit;
50
51 tree->fullpath = join_path(prefix, tree->name);
52
53 unit = strchr(tree->name, '@');
54 if (unit)
55 tree->basenamelen = unit - tree->name;
56 else
57 tree->basenamelen = strlen(tree->name);
58
59 for_each_child(tree, child)
60 fill_fullpaths(child, tree->fullpath);
61}

126static const char *guess_type_by_name(const char *fname, const char *fallback)
127{
128 const char *s;
129
130 s = strrchr(fname, '.');
131 if (s == NULL)
132 return fallback;
133 if (!strcasecmp(s, ".dts"))
134 return "dts";
135 if (!strcasecmp(s, ".dtb"))
136 return "dtb";
137 return fallback;
138}
139
140static const char *guess_input_format(const char *fname, const char *fallback)
141{
142 struct stat statbuf;
143 fdt32_t magic;
144 FILE *f;
145
146 if (stat(fname, &statbuf) != 0)
147 return fallback;
148
149 if (S_ISDIR(statbuf.st_mode))
150 return "fs";
151
152 if (!S_ISREG(statbuf.st_mode))
153 return fallback;
154
155 f = fopen(fname, "r");
156 if (f == NULL)
157 return fallback;
158 if (fread(&magic, 4, 1, f) != 1) {
159 fclose(f);
160 return fallback;
161 }
162 fclose(f);
163
164 if (fdt32_to_cpu(magic) == FDT_MAGIC)
165 return "dtb";
166
167 return guess_type_by_name(fname, fallback);
168}
169
170int main(int argc, char *argv[])
171{
172 struct dt_info *dti;
173 const char *inform = NULL;
174 const char *outform = NULL;
175 const char *outname = "-";
176 const char *depname = NULL;
177 bool force = false, sort = false;
178 const char *arg;
179 int opt;
180 FILE *outf = NULL;
181 int outversion = DEFAULT_FDT_VERSION;
182 long long cmdline_boot_cpuid = -1;
183
184 quiet = 0;
185 reservenum = 0;
186 minsize = 0;
187 padsize = 0;
188 alignsize = 0;
189
190 while ((opt = util_getopt_long()) != EOF) {
191 switch (opt) {
192 case 'I':
193 inform = optarg;
194 break;
195 case 'O':
196 outform = optarg;
197 break;
198 case 'o':
199 outname = optarg;
200 break;
201 case 'V':
202 outversion = strtol(optarg, NULL, 0);
203 break;
204 case 'd':
205 depname = optarg;
206 break;
207 case 'R':
208 reservenum = strtol(optarg, NULL, 0);
209 break;
210 case 'S':
211 minsize = strtol(optarg, NULL, 0);
212 break;
213 case 'p':
214 padsize = strtol(optarg, NULL, 0);
215 break;
216 case 'a':
217 alignsize = strtol(optarg, NULL, 0);
218 if (!is_power_of_2(alignsize))
219 die("Invalid argument \"%d\" to -a option\n",
220 alignsize);
221 break;
222 case 'f':
223 force = true;
224 break;
225 case 'q':
226 quiet++;
227 break;
228 case 'b':
229 cmdline_boot_cpuid = strtoll(optarg, NULL, 0);
230 break;
231 case 'i':
232 srcfile_add_search_path(optarg);
233 break;
234 case 'v':
235 util_version();
236 case 'H':
237 if (streq(optarg, "legacy"))
238 phandle_format = PHANDLE_LEGACY;
239 else if (streq(optarg, "epapr"))
240 phandle_format = PHANDLE_EPAPR;
241 else if (streq(optarg, "both"))
242 phandle_format = PHANDLE_BOTH;
243 else
244 die("Invalid argument \"%s\" to -H option\n",
245 optarg);
246 break;
247
248 case 's':
249 sort = true;
250 break;
251
252 case 'W':
253 parse_checks_option(true, false, optarg);
254 break;
255
256 case 'E':
257 parse_checks_option(false, true, optarg);
258 break;
259
260 case '@':
261 generate_symbols = 1;
262 break;
263 case 'A':
264 auto_label_aliases = 1;
265 break;
266
267 case 'h':
268 usage(NULL);
269 default:
270 usage("unknown option");
271 }
272 }
273
274 if (argc > (optind+1))
275 usage("missing files");
276 else if (argc < (optind+1))
277 arg = "-";
278 else
279 arg = argv[optind];
280
281 /* minsize and padsize are mutually exclusive */
282 if (minsize && padsize)
283 die("Can't set both -p and -S\n");
284
285 if (depname) {
286 depfile = fopen(depname, "w");
287 if (!depfile)
288 die("Couldn't open dependency file %s: %s\n", depname,
289 strerror(errno));
290 fprintf(depfile, "%s:", outname);
291 }
292
293 if (inform == NULL)
294 inform = guess_input_format(arg, "dts");
295 if (outform == NULL) {
296 outform = guess_type_by_name(outname, NULL);
297 if (outform == NULL) {
298 if (streq(inform, "dts"))
299 outform = "dtb";
300 else
301 outform = "dts";
302 }
303 }
304 if (streq(inform, "dts"))
305 dti = dt_from_source(arg);
306 else if (streq(inform, "fs"))
307 dti = dt_from_fs(arg);
308 else if(streq(inform, "dtb"))
309 dti = dt_from_blob(arg);
310 else
311 die("Unknown input format \"%s\"\n", inform);
312
313 dti->outname = outname;
314
315 if (depfile) {
316 fputc('\n', depfile);
317 fclose(depfile);
318 }
319
320 if (cmdline_boot_cpuid != -1)
321 dti->boot_cpuid_phys = cmdline_boot_cpuid;
322
323 fill_fullpaths(dti->dt, "");
324 process_checks(force, dti);
325
326 /* on a plugin, generate by default */
327 if (dti->dtsflags & DTSF_PLUGIN) {
328 generate_fixups = 1;
329 }
330
331 if (auto_label_aliases)
332 generate_label_tree(dti, "aliases", false);
333
334 if (generate_symbols)
335 generate_label_tree(dti, "__symbols__", true);
336
337 if (generate_fixups) {
338 generate_fixups_tree(dti, "__fixups__");
339 generate_local_fixups_tree(dti, "__local_fixups__");
340 }
341
342 if (sort)
343 sort_tree(dti);
344
345 if (streq(outname, "-")) {
346 outf = stdout;
347 } else {
348 outf = fopen(outname, "wb");
349 if (! outf)
350 die("Couldn't open output file %s: %s\n",
351 outname, strerror(errno));
352 }
353
354 if (streq(outform, "dts")) {
355 dt_to_source(outf, dti);
356 } else if (streq(outform, "dtb")) {
357 dt_to_blob(outf, dti, outversion);
358 } else if (streq(outform, "asm")) {
359 dt_to_asm(outf, dti, outversion);
360 } else if (streq(outform, "null")) {
361 /* do nothing */
362 } else {
363 die("Unknown output format \"%s\"\n", outform);
364 }
365
366 exit(0);
367}
